text: Han may refer to: == Ethnic groups == * Han Chinese, or Han People () == Former states == * Han dynasty (漢/汉) (206 BC – 220 AD), a dynasty split into two eras, Western Han and Eastern Han * Daehan Jaeguk or Korean Empire () (1897–1910), the last monarchial kingdom of Korea. == Languages == * Han Chinese language, or just Chinese * Hangul (한글 Hangeul), the Korean alphabet * Hanja (한자, 漢字), Han characters used for the Korean language ==Other uses== * Khan (title), or Han (汗) in Chinese transliteration, originally Central Asian title for a sovereign or military ruler * Han Solo, a character in the Star Wars franchise
title: Han
